{"tid":1784524,"cid":18,"subCid":6,"title":"[支爆] 推背圖揭示中共滅亡","createTime":"2019-12-15T17:20:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T17:42:21.000Z","uid":309553,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb846b7aa6c490f971408ef9a5db786220c8048","tid":1784524,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:20:09.000Z","msg":"好多人覺得推背圖只係後世穿鑿附會<br />\n即使係真，有講法話30幾象之後都已經打亂晒<br />\n而且網上就算同一象都有好多種唔同解法，唔知邊個係真<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NSPHHZtfVTY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNSPHHZtfVTY&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=a1345a00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NSPHHZtfVTY</a><br />\n呢個channel之前喺連登見有人po過出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hgrHRWmcN4w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhgrHRWmcN4w&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=1919932e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hgrHRWmcN4w</a><br />\n同其他解推背圖嘅人唔同，佢嘅解法係可以apply到其他象，而唔似大紀元果d飛機文咁 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/4HfLM026KMk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F4HfLM026KMk&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=ae64413d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/4HfLM026KMk</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MOQE76M2jQU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMOQE76M2jQU&d=tTL%2BVp%2FfZAnEQ6lEIPL8hgsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=a421d04e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MOQE76M2jQU</a><br />\n43象離我哋好近，可能係呢三四年嘅事，姐係2023-2024年會發生"},{"pid":"cdeee41ed1ec79fef08a70e8ac19786200ab06dd","tid":1784524,"uid":309553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:20:56.000Z","msg":"有冇人好鍾意睇推背圖，一齊入嚟吹下水"},{"pid":"d0473ea29b61ec52ca1404155ec5194aef4baeab","tid":1784524,"uid":43556,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:21:38.000Z","msg":"去神秘台啦屌"},{"pid":"60